  "title": "IASA 2025 Year in Review",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"ContentPanel\" id=\"mainContentWrapper\">\n<div data-height-offset=\"true\" id=\"masterMainBreadcrumb\"></div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_UserMessagesUpdatePanel\">\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_PublishUpdatePanel\">\n</div><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1___Drag\" style=\"display:none;position:absolute;z-index:32000;filter:alpha(opacity=75);\">\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\">\n<div class=\"WebPartZone\" id=\"WebPartZone1_Page1\">\n<div class=\"iMIS-WebPart\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\" id=\"ste_container_ciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca\"><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1_gwpciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca_ciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca_Panel_NewContentHtml\">\n<h2>IASA 2025 Year in Review</h2>\n<p>The strength of IASA comes from our community — and 2025 showcased that more than ever. With rising membership, deeper volunteer engagement, expanded educational opportunities, and new ways to connect, this year marked significant steps forward. Explore our 2025 Year in Review to see the progress we made together.</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"iMIS-WebPart\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\" id=\"ste_container_ciNewContentHtml3_029fc86ca7e24f44a97dce4604650c77\"><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1_gwpciNewContentHtml3_029fc86ca7e24f44a97dce4604650c77_ciNewContentHtml3_029fc86ca7e24f44a97dce4604650c77_Panel_NewContentHtml3\">\n<div style=\"margin:0px auto; position:relative; height:0; overflow:hidden; max-width:816px; padding-bottom:1056px;\"></div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_downloadContainer\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_HiddenDownloadPathField\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage1$HiddenDownloadPathField\" type=\"hidden\"/><input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_dow